comments: Randle (NYK) wraps Embiid (PHI) in the post.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Barrett's (NYK) body as he dislodges the ball.
During the pick, Simmons (PHI) and Gibson (NYK) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Randle (NYK) makes marginal contact with Embiid (PHI) off ball that does not affect his FOM.
Gibson (NYK) makes marginal contact with Harris's (PHI) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Barrett (NYK) that does not prevent him from getting to the pass.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Randle (NYK) during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Morris Sr. (NYK) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Korkmaz (PHI) makes marginal contact with Ntilikina's (NYK) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) sets the screen in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (PHI) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Embiid (PHI) initiates some contact with Randle (NYK) in the post, but the contact is marginal.
Harris (PHI) sets the screen in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.
Randle (NYK) sets the screen in Ennis III's (PHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ennis III (PHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Ellington (NYK) after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Ntilikina (NYK) commits a take foul on Korkmaz (PHI).
Harris (PHI) makes more than marginal contact with Randle (NYK) during his shooting motion on his driving shot attempt.
Korkmaz (PHI) is firming up in a screening position in Barrett's (NYK) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Gibson (NYK) makes incidental contact with Simmons (PHI) during the rebound.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes contact with Ennis III's (PHI) head on the driving shot attempt.
